high_descs: Turn right and go to the countertop to your right.
Pick up the bowl closest to the sink on the countertop.
Turn left, walk straight past the countertop, then go to the toilet room to your right and turn to the sink to your left.
Put the bowl in the sink, fill it with water and then pick it up.
Turn left, get out of the toilet room, head to the sofa and then go to the dresser to your left.
Put the bowl with the water on the left corner of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl filled with water on a dresser.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the countertop on your right the microwave and the sink on it.
Pick up the bowl on the countertop.
Take a left at the end of the counter take a right and go into the bathroom on the right and go to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink turn the water on and take the bowl out.
Leave the bathroom and go to the dresser under the TV on your left.
Place the bowl of water on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl of water on the dresser under the tv.
